		<div class="article inside">
	
	<h1>Snook++</h1>
		<p>Things have been crazy busy for the past couple weeks and for good reason. I've mentioned before that my wife and I were in the process of adopting. Last Wednesday, the day we've been working towards for almost two years had finally arrived: to be parents once again.</p>
<p>Lucas Adam James  has become the latest addition to the Snook clan and we couldn't be happier. Our deepest gratitude to the birthmom who allowed us to be in the room during the birth, which was absolutely incredible. To be sure, it will be a day I will never forget.</p>
<p>After spending a week in Kansas, we're heading on to Chicago for a few days before our return home to Canada. We're looking forward to getting back home and settle into our new routine. </p>
<p>Anyways, just thought I'd share the good news! </p>	
</div>
